#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text040"
msgid ""
"The history of the royal family of Hyrule\n"
"is also the history of Calamity Ganon, <1.ra>a primal evil that has "
"endured over the ages."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text041"
msgid ""
"This evil has been turned back time and time again<1.ra>by a warrior "
"wielding the soul of a hero, and a\n"
"princess who carries the blood of the Goddess."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text042"
msgid ""
"With the passage of time, each conflict\n"
"with Ganon faded into legend.<1.ra>So listen closely as I tell you of "
"this\n"
"\"legend\" that occurred 10,000 years ago."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text043"
msgid ""
"Hyrule was then blossoming as\n"
"a highly advanced civilization.<1.ra>Even the most powerful monsters "
"posed\n"
"little threat to the denizens of the realm."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text044"
msgid ""
"The people thought it wise to utilize\n"
"their technological prowess<1.ra>to ensure the safety of the land,\n"
"should Calamity Ganon ever return."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text045"
msgid ""
"They constructed four mechanical wonders\n"
"that came to be known as the Divine Beasts.<1.ra>They also built a legion"
" of autonomous\n"
"weapons called Guardians."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text046"
msgid ""
"The Divine Beasts were piloted by four individuals\n"
"of exceptional skill from across the land.<1.ra>And thus, the plan to "
"neutralize Ganon was forged."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text047"
msgid ""
"Upon Ganon's inevitable return to Hyrule, <1.ra>the princess and the hero"
" fought alongside these\n"
"four Champions against this ancient evil."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text048"
msgid ""
"The Guardians were tasked with protecting the hero<1.ra>as the Divine "
"Beasts unleashed a furious attack upon\n"
"their terrible foe."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo105_0_Text049"
msgid ""
"And when the hero wielding the sword that\n"
"seals the darkness delivered his final blow...<1.ra>The princess used her"
" sacred power\n"
"to seal away Calamity Ganon."
msgstr ""

